  "prompt": "Who is best in Sachin, virat and dhoni?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" among Sachin Tendulkar, Virat Kohli, and MS Dhoni depends on the criteria you're considering, as each of them excelled in different aspects of cricket and in different roles.\n\n1. **Sachin Tendulkar**: Often referred to as the \"God of Cricket,\" Tendulkar is celebrated for his classical batting style, consistent performance over two decades, and numerous records, including being the highest run-scorer in international cricket. His technical skill and ability to perform under pressure have made him a cricketing icon.\n\n2. **Virat Kohli**: Known for his aggressive batting style and fitness, Kohli is one of the best modern-day cricketers. He is celebrated for his ability to chase down scores and his consistency across all formats. Kohli has a remarkable record in ODIs and T20s and is also among the top run-scorers in Tests.\n\n3. **MS Dhoni**: As a captain, Dhoni led India to victories in the ICC T20 World Cup (2007), ICC Cricket World Cup (2011), and ICC Champions Trophy (2013). Known for his calm demeanor and strategic mind, he is one of the best finishers in limited-overs cricket and a highly respected leader.\n\nIn summary: \n- **For pure technical batting skills and iconic status**, Sachin Tendulkar often leads.\n- **For modern, aggressive batting and chasing capabilities**, Virat Kohli is frequently hailed.\n- **For leadership, finishing games, and wicketkeeping skills**, MS Dhoni is unparalleled.\n\nChoosing the \"best\" can be subjective and depends on personal preferences and values in cricket.",
